   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_Harvard_604757_1845-04_page01.jpg"/>
            <p>that the publishers of New York<lb/>
                    have sent <persName ref="./Personography.xml#PortJ1">Miss Porter</persName> a memo<lb/>
                    deal of American gratitude<lb/>
                    and appreciation of <unclear>merit</unclear>
               <lb/>
                    - An arm chair I think the<lb/>
                    newspapers say they sent her<lb/>
                    - It would gratify me much<lb/>
                    even to have the top of <del>a table</del>
               <lb/>
                    a little table of American<lb/>
                    wood as a memorial of<lb/>
               <gap/>
               <unclear>portion</unclear> of your <unclear>Towns</unclear>
               <lb/>
               <pb n="2" facs="Edgeworth_Harvard_604757_1845-04_page02.jpg"/>
                    
                    and form the Board of Works<lb/>
                    in <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#London_ENK">London</placeName> to <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Hong-Kong_CN">
                  <choice>
                     <orig>Hong Cong</orig>
                     <reg>Hong Kong</reg>
                  </choice>
               </placeName>
               <lb/>
                    I want nothing for him from<lb/>
                    you but your good wishes<lb/>
                    and he wants nothing<lb/>
                    but to pay his respects to my<lb/>
                    friend <persName ref="./Personography.xml#RedX1">Mr. Redstone</persName>
               <lb/>
            </p>
            <closer>
                    I am yours sincerely<lb/>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Maria Edgeworth</persName>
               <lb/>
               <dateline>
                  <date when="1845-04-08"/>April 8<hi rend="superscript">h</hi> 1845</dateline>
               <lb/>
               <lb/>
            </closer>
         </div>
      </body>
